data.name: DeleteClaim
data.value:
DISABLE TRIGGER t_del_claim_status ON [dbo].[scs_claims] GO DISABLE TRIGGER [t_del_claim_det_status] ON [dbo].[scs_claim_parts] GO DISABLE TRIGGER [tr_delete_claim_details_history] ON [dbo].[scs_claim_details] GO
DECLARE @claimNumber varchar(16) = '{ClaimNumber}' DECLARE @ClaimId int , @NoteID int , @IncomingDocumentDetailId int , @DetailId int , @IdField int
SELECT @ClaimId = [iclaim_id] FROM [dbo].[scs_claims] WHERE [sclaim_number] = @claimNumber
select @NoteID = inote_id from [dbo].[scs_claim_comments] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
select @IncomingDocumentDetailId = [iincoming_detail_id] from [dbo].[scs_document_incoming_detail] where imodule_key_id = @ClaimId AND idoc_module_id = 1
delete from [dbo].[scs_check_entry] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_comment_user_access_history] where inote_id = @NoteID
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_comment_user_access] where inote_id = @NoteID
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_comments] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_credit_payments_history] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_credit_payments] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_jobs] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_parts] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_payees] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
DELETE FROM scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access_history FROM scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access_history INNER JOIN scs_document_incoming_detail AS d ON d.iincoming_detail_id = scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access_history.iincoming_detail_id WHERE (d.imodule_key_id = @ClaimId) AND (d.idoc_module_id = 1)
DELETE FROM scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access FROM scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access INNER JOIN scs_document_incoming_detail AS d ON d.iincoming_detail_id = scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access.iincoming_detail_id WHERE (d.imodule_key_id = @ClaimId) AND (d.idoc_module_id = 1)
delete from [dbo].[scs_document_incoming_detail] where imodule_key_id = @ClaimId AND idoc_module_id = 1
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_document_outgoing_detail] where imodule_key_id = @ClaimId AND idoc_module_id = 1
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_details_history] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_inspection_history] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_inspections] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement_history] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement_loss_codes] where iclaim_id = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_survey_data] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_service_authorization] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
EXEC p_insert_db_session_info 'apiuser', 5
delete from [dbo].[scs_claim_details] where [iclaim_id] = @ClaimId
delete from [dbo].[scs_claims] where sclaim_number = @claimNumber
select @IdField =max(iref_pay_number) from [dbo].[scs_check_entry] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_check_entry, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(icomment_user_access_history_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_comment_user_access_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_comment_user_access_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(icomment_user_access_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_comment_user_access] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_comment_user_access, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(inote_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_comments] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_comments, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(ipayment_history_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_credit_payments_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_credit_payments_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(ipayment_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_credit_payments] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_credit_payments, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(ijob_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_jobs] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_jobs, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(idetail_part_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_parts] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_parts, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(ipayee_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_payees] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_payees, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(idocument_incoming_detail_user_access_history_id) from [dbo].[scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(idocument_incoming_detail_user_access_id) from [dbo].[scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_document_incoming_detail_user_access, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iincoming_detail_id) from [dbo].[scs_document_incoming_detail] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_document_incoming_detail, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_settlement_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_settlement, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(ioutgoing_detail_id) from [dbo].[scs_document_outgoing_detail] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_document_outgoing_detail, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_history_det_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_details_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_details_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_inspection_history_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_inspection_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_inspection_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_inspection_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_inspections] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_inspections, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_settlement_history_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement_history] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_settlement_history, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_settlement_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_settlement, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_loss_code_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_settlement_loss_codes] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_settlement_loss_codes, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(idetail_id) from [dbo].[scs_claim_details] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claim_details, RESEED, @IdField)
select @IdField =max(iclaim_id) from [dbo].[scs_claims] DBCC CHECKIDENT (scs_claims, RESEED, @IdField)
GO ENABLE TRIGGER t_del_claim_status ON [dbo].[scs_claims] GO ENABLE TRIGGER [t_del_claim_det_status] ON [dbo].[scs_claim_parts] GO ENABLE TRIGGER [tr_delete_claim_details_history] ON [dbo].[scs_claim_details]
